attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of furniture. They start by screwing together the sidebars, then the base frames. Once the sidebars are mounted on the base frames, they insert the bottom tray and screw it in place. Next, they insert the middle tray and screw it in place. Finally, they insert the top tray and screw it in place. They then mount the wheels on the bottom of the base.
